  <brief_title>Study Evaluating Piperacillin-Tazobactam on Certain Bacteria in Hematology and Oncology Units</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Piperacillin-Tazobactam Use on the Prevalence Rate of Extended-Spectrum Beta-Lactamase (ESBL) Producing Escherichia Coli and Klebsiella Pneumoniae in Hematology and Oncology Units.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
